    "On a trip between Rome and Assisi, he chanced to read <em>De la po\u00e9sie chr\u00e9tienne</em> (1836) by <a href=\"/rioa\">Alexis-Fran\u00e7ois Rio</a>, a volume owned by the French sculptor, F\u00e9licie de Fauveau.": [],
    "She introduced Lindsay to the spiritual reception of the arts, the <em>\u00e9cole Mystique</em>, whom the two saw particularly in the work of Benozzo Gozzoli's frescoes at San Gimignano.": [],
